column5: We will be fishing June 16-24 in northwest area by camp narrows. Any info on walleye bite would be helpfull.
it doesnt mater how the fishing is becuase I will win the big money pool for the week joe mac

fished the NW arm Memorial Day weekend stayed at Labbells. walleyes were very slow and scatered. Try Browns inlet trolling spiners. However the smallies were biting in Alexandria Bay. LOL and Get Bit.
